# helix.fhir.client.sdk

Fluent API to call the FHIR server that handles: 1. Authentication to FHIR server 2. Renewing access token when they expire 3. Retry when there are transient errors 4. Un-bundling the resources received from FHIR server 5. Paging 6. Streaming 7. Logging 8. Simulating a $graph call when the server does not support it # Usage `pip install helix.fhir.client.sdk` # Documentation https://icanbwell.github.io/helix.fhir.client.sdk/ # Test Project using this https://github.com/icanbwell/fhir-server-performance
info.name: helix.fhir.client.sdk
